          <h1>Rope Tool</h1>
          <h3>January 2023 - Present</h3><br>
          <p class="top">This is the project that I am currently working on! Rope Tool is an ongoing passion project that I'm lucky to have been able to share the development of with my close friends. Our goal is to publically release it when it's ready, over the course of development I've had to work on several aspects to the game. I was originally brought on to help develop the game's zero gravity physics alongside the unique player controls. I've also been soley in charge of Rope Tool's sound design. Finally as of June 2023, I have taken over as the lead level designer for the remainder of Rope Tool's development.</p>
          <p><a href="https://xandergoodwin.itch.io/rope-tool"class="viewLink">Click Here to play Rope Tool</a></p>
      </div>

