      <div class="subtext">
          <h1>Bullet Hell Basketball</h1>
          <h3>January 2022 - May 2022</h3><br>
          <p class="top">If there is one game you must check out, it has to be this one. Developed in Unity, Bullet Hell Basketball is one the most polished projects I've had the pleasure of working on. Working in a group of 4, I was tasked with developing the Menu, Pause, and Graphics UI. The assets for most were created in Adobe Photoshop and then imported to Unity where scripting was added to provide proper function. Additionally, I lent a hand in the scripting needed for Player Movement and designed additional gamemodes such as the tutorial and Swipe Shot Rally.</p>
          <p><a href="https://simmer.io/@nickybakes/bullet-hell-basketball"class="viewLink">Click Here to Play Bullet Hell Basketball</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="subimg">
          <img src="/assets/img/stationary.png" alt="Screenshot from Stationary">
