      <div class="subtext">
          <h1>Crunch Time</h1>
          <h3>February 2020 - April 2020</h3><br>
          <p class="top">Crunch Time was my first venture into the Monogame framework for Visual Studio. Inspired by the time mechanics of Superhot, the game is a top down shooter where you have to clear waves of enemies in different rooms. However, the speed of both your bullets and the enemy's bullets are determined by how fast you're moving. Figuring out the math required to rotate and orient the player character as well as the speed modifications is still one of the most challenging project undertakings I have worked on! With my controls, my teammates would then develop levels using the level editor we also developed.</p>
      </div>
