          <h1>Walter Dating Simulator</h1>
          <h3>October 2019</h3><br>
          <p class="top">Aside from a few apps I had made in years prior, I consider the Walter Dating Simulator to be the first game I have ever made. It is simultaneously the best and the worst piece of media that I have ever created. I don't know how I made it. I don't want to know how I made it. I simply woke up in a cold sweat one morning with vague memories of making this application. Jokes aside, even though this game hasn't aged as well as my other projects, I still enjoy the humor I went for.</p>
