          <h3>September 2021</h3><br>
          <p class="top">Developed using Tabletop Simulator, me and a team of three others developed a small card game using lore from the Athame series. The objectivbe of the game is to collect cards and build a ritual circle all while using other spells to sabotage other players. My primary role in this project was to come up with secondary card effects that would create engaging moments of sabotage and fun between players.</p>
